# paper-autopilot-open script credentials
# Alternative to ~/.claude/paper-autopilot-open/config.json  ->  "api_keys": { ... }
#
# Copy this file to `scripts/.env` and fill in ONLY the keys the features you use need.
# Resolution order for every key: (1) config.json api_keys -> (2) this scripts/.env -> (3) process env.
#
# Which key each script actually uses:
#   GEMINI_API_KEY      PPT image generation (scripts/ppt/generate_ppt_slides.js)
#                       AND RAG embeddings when embedding.provider = "gemini"
#                       (scripts/ingest/*, scripts/retrieve.mjs)
#   OPENAI_API_KEY      RAG embeddings when embedding.provider = "openai"
#                       (scripts/ingest/*, scripts/retrieve.mjs)
#   STORM_PARSE_API_KEY document parsing (scripts/parse/storm_parse.py)
#   TAVILY_API_KEY      reference-image web search for PPT (generate_ppt_slides.js --ref)
#
# Leave a key blank/unset if you don't use that feature.

GEMINI_API_KEY=
OPENAI_API_KEY=
STORM_PARSE_API_KEY=
TAVILY_API_KEY=
